* [[Julie White]]: Judy Witwicky
* [[Isabel Lucas]]: Alice
* [[Glenn Morshower]]: General Morshower
* [[John Benjamin Hickey]]: Theodore Galloway
* [[Rainn Wilson]]: Professor Colan
* [[Matthew Marsden]]: Graham
* [[Deep Roy]]: Grenzbeamter
* [[Spencer Garrett]]: Generalstabschef der US Air Force
'''Transformers (Stimmen/Original):'''
* [[Peter Cullen]]: Optimus Prime
* [[Tony Todd]]: The Fallen
* [[Hugo Weaving]]: Megatron
* [[Mark Ryan]]: Jetfire
* [[Jess Harnell]]: Ironhide
