* [[Bruce Hopkins]]: Gamling
* [[Sean Bean]]: [[Figuren in Tolkiens Welt#Boromir|Boromir]]&lt;ref name=&quot;Ext&quot;&gt;Extended Version&lt;/ref&gt;
* [[John Noble]]: [[Figuren in Tolkiens Welt#Denethor|Denethor]]&lt;ref name=&quot;Ext&quot; /&gt;
* [[Paris Howe Strewe]]: Theodred
* [[Jed Brophy]]: Sharku
* [[Jed Brophy]]: Snaga
